"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_women's_national_soccer_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_women's_national_soccer_team\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a great manager\", \"from\": 1356, \"to\": 1371}, {\"ngram\": \"gold\", \"from\": 1383, \"to\": 1387}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 1391, \"to\": 1400}, {\"ngram\": \"a great start\", \"from\": 1404, \"to\": 1417}, {\"ngram\": \"her journey\", \"from\": 1421, \"to\": 1432}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But the Olympics was quite difficult for the Spanish, who included many of the former Barcelona team-mates I have just left behind.\", \"from\": 1453, \"to\": 1584, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1498, \"end\": 1505, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain\", \"score\": 0.6318898062123348, \"rank\": 0.5812734657517674, \"text\": \"Spanish\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain\"}, {\"begin\": 1539, \"end\": 1548, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/FC_Barcelona\", \"score\": 0.9999999526439762, \"rank\": 4.7268847799077415e-08, \"text\": \"Barcelona\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/FC_Barcelona\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/FC_Barcelona\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 1457, \"to\": 1469}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The truth is players like Aitana Bonmati, Alexia Putellas and Salma Paralluelo, some of the very best footballers in the women's game, did not get to show their quality as they would have hoped to.\", \"from\": 1586, \"to\": 1783, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1612, \"end\": 1626, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aitana_Bonmat\\u00ed\", \"score\": 0.9999999905639925, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Aitana Bonmati\", \"types\": [\"Q937857\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aitana_Bonmat\\u00ed\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aitana_Bonmat\\u00ed\"}, {\"begin\": 1628, \"end\": 1643, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alexia_Putellas\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Alexia Putellas\", \"types\": [\"Q937857\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alexia_Putellas\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alexia_Putellas\"}, {\"begin\": 1648, \"end\": 1664, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Salma_Paralluelo\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Salma Paralluelo\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Salma_Paralluelo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Salma_Paralluelo\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The truth\", \"from\": 1586, \"to\": 1595}, {\"ngram\": \"players\", \"from\": 1599, \"to\": 1606}, {\"ngram\": \"the very best footballers\", \"from\": 1674, \"to\": 1699}, {\"ngram\": \"the women's game\", \"from\": 1703, \"to\": 1719}, {\"ngram\": \"their quality\", \"from\": 1741, \"to\": 1754}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And that is because the programme at an Olympic football tournament is so relentless.\", \"from\": 1785, \"to\": 1870, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the programme\", \"from\": 1805, \"to\": 1818}, {\"ngram\": \"an Olympic football tournament\", \"from\": 1822, \"to\": 1852}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Not only are you required to play every three days after a gruelling season but you also have to travel a big country like France to do so.\", \"from\": 1871, \"to\": 2010, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1994, \"end\": 2000, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9996752144183321, \"rank\": 0.00032489106577635024, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a gruelling season\", \"from\": 1928, \"to\": 1946}, {\"ngram\": \"a big country\", \"from\": 1975, \"to\": 1988}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And on top that there can be extra-time and penalties too.\", \"from\": 2011, \"to\": 2069, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"top\", \"from\": 2018, \"to\": 2021}, {\"ngram\": \"extra-time\", \"from\": 2040, \"to\": 2050}, {\"ngram\": \"penalties\", \"from\": 2055, \"to\": 2064}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Nobody plays every three days like that in the normal season, so I do not know why that has to be the case at a Games.\", \"from\": 2070, \"to\": 2188, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Nobody\", \"from\": 2070, \"to\": 2076}, {\"ngram\": \"the normal season\", \"from\": 2113, \"to\": 2130}, {\"ngram\": \"the case\", \"from\": 2168, \"to\": 2176}, {\"ngram\": \"a Games\", \"from\": 2180, \"to\": 2187}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I was watching Spain thinking 'that looks painful'.\", \"from\": 2190, \"to\": 2241, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2205, \"end\": 2210, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9266039800929909, \"rank\": 0.07920969611985078, \"text\": \"Spain\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain_national_football_team\"}], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It must have been excruciating to push your body like that.\", \"from\": 2242, \"to\": 2301, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"your body\", \"from\": 2281, \"to\": 2290}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The physical output involved is huge and there is not a load of recovery time.\", \"from\": 2302, \"to\": 2380, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The physical output\", \"from\": 2302, \"to\": 2321}, {\"ngram\": \"a load\", \"from\": 2356, \"to\": 2362}, {\"ngram\": \"recovery time\", \"from\": 2366, \"to\": 2379}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For me, Spain are the best footballing side around but it was clear how much they were struggling, and they were not the only ones.\", \"from\": 2381, \"to\": 2512, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2389, \"end\": 2394, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9266039800929909, \"rank\": 0.07920969611985078, \"text\": \"Spain\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain_national_football_team\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the best footballing side\", \"from\": 2399, \"to\": 2424}, {\"ngram\": \"the only ones\", \"from\": 2498, \"to\": 2511}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The US, though, had the fresher players because they are midway through the NWSL campaign back in the States so they were the ones able to see out games, such as the final, where they beat Brazil 1-0 at Parc des Princes while Spain lost the bronze-medal match with Germany.\", \"from\": 2514, \"to\": 2787, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2518, \"end\": 2520, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"score\": 0.9999979369057109, \"rank\": 2.0611072206909036e-06, \"text\": \"US\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\"}, {\"begin\": 2590, \"end\": 2594, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Women's_Soccer_League\", \"score\": 0.9999999999376996, \"rank\": 6.226830791009859e-11, \"text\": \"NWSL\", \"types\": [\"Q623109\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Women's_Soccer_League\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Women's_Soccer_League\"}, {\"begin\": 2703, \"end\": 2709, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.8789953630562295, \"rank\": 0.13766239097020044, \"text\": \"Brazil\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 2717, \"end\": 2733, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Parc_des_Princes\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Parc des Princes\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Parc_des_Princes\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Parc_des_Princes\"}, {\"begin\": 2740, \"end\": 2745, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9266039800929909, \"rank\": 0.07920969611985078, \"text\": \"Spain\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 2779, \"end\": 2786, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Germany_women's_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.5610117541881181, \"rank\": 0.7824938471038352, \"text\": \"Germany\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Germany_women's_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Germany_women's_national_football_team\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the fresher players\", \"from\": 2534, \"to\": 2553}, {\"ngram\": \"the States\", \"from\": 2612, \"to\": 2622}, {\"ngram\": \"the ones\", \"from\": 2636, \"to\": 2644}, {\"ngram\": \"games\", \"from\": 2661, \"to\": 2666}, {\"ngram\": \"the bronze-medal match\", \"from\": 2751, \"to\": 2773}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Maybe the story in Paris would have been Marta signing off with gold at the age of 38 instead of a third Olympic silver medal.\", \"from\": 2789, \"to\": 2915, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2808, \"end\": 2813, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999995453, \"rank\": 5.400267762323021e-13, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the story\", \"from\": 2795, \"to\": 2804}, {\"ngram\": \"Marta\", \"from\": 2830, \"to\": 2835}, {\"ngram\": \"gold\", \"from\": 2853, \"to\": 2857}, {\"ngram\": \"the age\", \"from\": 2861, \"to\": 2868}, {\"ngram\": \"a third Olympic silver medal\", \"from\": 2886, \"to\": 2914}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But that result does not take away from her story.\", \"from\": 2916, \"to\": 2966, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"that result\", \"from\": 2920, \"to\": 2931}, {\"ngram\": \"her story\", \"from\": 2956, \"to\": 2965}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Any player would be happy to have achieved just a quarter of what she's done in the game.\", \"from\": 2967, \"to\": 3056, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Any player\", \"from\": 2967, \"to\": 2977}, {\"ngram\": \"just a quarter\", \"from\": 3010, \"to\": 3024}, {\"ngram\": \"the game\", \"from\": 3047, \"to\": 3055}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She has been the driving force in Brazilian women's football.\", \"from\": 3057, \"to\": 3118, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the driving force\", \"from\": 3070, \"to\": 3087}, {\"ngram\": \"Brazilian women's football\", \"from\": 3091, \"to\": 3117}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Marta has long been an inspiration of mine - her quality on the ball is unmatched and she will go down as one of, if not the greatest to have played the women's game.\", \"from\": 3120, \"to\": 3286, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Marta\", \"from\": 3120, \"to\": 3125}, {\"ngram\": \"an inspiration\", \"from\": 3140, \"to\": 3154}, {\"ngram\": \"mine\", \"from\": 3158, \"to\": 3162}, {\"ngram\": \"her quality\", \"from\": 3165, \"to\": 3176}, {\"ngram\": \"the ball\", \"from\": 3180, \"to\": 3188}, {\"ngram\": \"the women's game\", \"from\": 3269, \"to\": 3285}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As she has got older, she has lost none of the ability to inspire her team-mates.\", \"from\": 3288, \"to\": 3369, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"none\", \"from\": 3323, \"to\": 3327}, {\"ngram\": \"the ability\", \"from\": 3331, \"to\": 3342}, {\"ngram\": \"her team-mates\", \"from\": 3354, \"to\": 3368}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She still wants to be there at 38 and that acts as a motivation for me.\", \"from\": 3370, \"to\": 3441, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a motivation\", \"from\": 3421, \"to\": 3433}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It makes me feel just the same.\", \"from\": 3442, \"to\": 3473, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But there are not always fairytale endings in sport, as we saw with Marta.\", \"from\": 3475, \"to\": 3549, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"fairytale endings\", \"from\": 3500, \"to\": 3517}, {\"ngram\": \"sport\", \"from\": 3521, \"to\": 3526}, {\"ngram\": \"Marta\", \"from\": 3543, \"to\": 3548}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I also know Spain's time will come again.\", \"from\": 3550, \"to\": 3591, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3562, \"end\": 3567, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9266039800929909, \"rank\": 0.07920969611985078, \"text\": \"Spain\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain_national_football_team\"}], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I'M so pleased to be at Chelsea and back in England and the Women's Super League.\", \"from\": 3593, \"to\": 3674, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3617, \"end\": 3624, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chelsea_F.C._Women\", \"score\": 0.9999831537479807, \"rank\": 1.6846535767761185e-05, \"text\": \"Chelsea\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\